5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[突發] 呀爺驚驚大反BNO平權？不如建議係英國郊區起個EcoCity作姊妹城市<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第一次開呢類po，如果個po持續到落去希望資深巴打大執個排版同用字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24042e4a8444e5fa5a77a7827f460eab228e377","tid":1482620,"uid":94312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"而以下完全係個人見解，唔放#1<br />\n<br />\n現時bno被當二等公民，係需要補償。我認為bno巴打溫和平權既另一種方向可以係向英國claim番一個土地，甚至係英屬海外既荒島，可以好似澳洲咁樣，以君主立憲既形式，得到外交手腕，亦可以有主權。<br />\n<br />\n同時，bno係中國以外領土立國，同港獨完全拉唔上關係，2047後亦可能無爭拗，真正脫離中共。<br />\n<br />\n不過利申我讀工程，完全9up, 錯左屌細力d<br />\n<br />\n代巴打po:<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=6dee5a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"af165cbe1e79fb9f635c969250aa831f47cccaa9","tid":1482620,"uid":94312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmh8kXE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftmh8kXE.png&h=af385a77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55jbiKk.png\" 